            <title>[SOLR-16453] overseer doesn&apos;t handle prs messages properly</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-16453</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Overseer thread doesn&apos;t process prs message properly. It gives preference to prs message, but then it drops other messages at that time.&lt;/p&gt;

